msgSnippet: Thank you very much for an excellent resource. I ll be playing with your font for quite a while. I especially appreciate your releasing the FontForge file; I
messageBody:
Thank you very much for an excellent resource. I'll be playing with your font for quite a while.

   I especially appreciate your releasing the FontForge file; I won't be using that myself, but I really like having that sort of thing around for those who have the time.

   I have changed the file name of your PDF file (removed some spaces around hyphens) so that the PDF extension will show.
